copy script src cdn first line & paste beore script src

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.js"></script>


(*)What is bootstrap?
Bootstrap is a free, open source front-end development framework for the creation of websites and web apps. Designed to enable responsive development
Bootstrap provides a collection of syntax for template designs.
Bootstrap 5 is the newest version of Bootstrap

-----input
<input type="text"  class="form-control" />
-----input border size & color
<input type="text" class=" border-3 border-success||border-dark||border-primary " />
------Text
    <div class="fs-1 fw-bold text-capitalize text-decoration-line-through">sandeep</div>
     fs => font size (1 to 6)
     fw=> font weight (bold,bolder,normal,light,italic)
     fst=> font style()
     text-capitalize||uppercase||lowercase
     w-25||50||75||100  => width
     p  => padding

-----Wrap
    text-wrap(Wrap text with) & text-nowrap (This text should overflow the parent)

-----heading alignment 
<h3 class="text-start|| text-center|| text-end ">
-----heading color 
<h3 class=" text-primary|| text-secondary|| text-danger">


-----radio& checkbox
<input type="radio" class="form-check-input"/>
<input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input " />
------select
<select name="district" class="form-select ">
-----file
<input type="file" class="form-control "/>


-----------Button
----Button color
<button class="btn btn-primary    btn-success    btn-danger">
----button outline
<button class="btn btn-outline-primary  btn-outline-danger ">
-----button size 
    .btn-lg or .btn-sm



-------Border
<div class=" border||border-bottom border-5  border-danger" >

------noWrap
<p class="text-nowrap">


-----Grid
bootstrap grid system allows upto 12 columns across the page (= one row)
 <div class="row">
        <div class="col-3"> <img src="./img/tiger.jpg"/></div>
        <div class="col-3"><p> Lorem ipsum dol</p></div>
      </div>

----BreakPoints
it is responsive
responssively arrange HTML elements depending the screen size 
xtra small      xs    for phones
small	          sm	  for tablets
medium	        md    small laptops
large	          lg	  laptop & desktops
extra large	    xl	  
xtra xtra large	xxl   

<div class="text-lg-start text-sm-center text-xl-end">
<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">

